    <p>4.- Open the <strong>MvcInAction solution file(MvcInAction.sln)</strong> and restore all the missing packages usin NuGet package manager.</p>
    <p>5.- Open the <strong>Package Manager Console</strong> and update the LocalDB database running the following command:</p>
    <blockquote>
        <p><em>update-database</em></p>
